st really gifted, only instead of being good at music or math I'm good at sleeping late.\n\n- Elizabeth Jane Howard, Mr Wrong\n|\nI don't think I really have any wisdom. Stay out of trouble. Good luck. Stay away from women because they will burn you, haha.\n\n- Jason\n|\nI burn a hole through everything I stare, and it happens when I stand in front of the mirror too.\n\n- Akshay\n|\nEven if all our senses fail to function − eyes turn blind and ears fail to listen − the heart will still listen, see and beat.\n\n- Kcat Yarza, KCAT CAN: I have a pen that writes\n|\nYou hold an absence at your center, as if it were a life.\n\n- Richard\n|\nIf you help someones bank account rise But you can't help their heart feel... Really, what is your value?\n\n- Nikki\n|\nSo long as the global economy continues to recover, that remains Obama's No. 1 claim to successful leadership. Nothing else even comes close.\n\n- Thomas\n|\nYou want power-either because you've already had a taste of it and want more, or because you've been made to feel powerless for too long.\n\n- Jennifer Lynn Barnes, All In\n|\nLearn to be brave and adventurous because you’ll never discover your place in the world, if you’re too afraid to leave your own backyard.\n\n- Nina\n|\nIf the bro army and sky army broke into war, I would die from the chose to fight for.\n\n- Sebastian\n|\nSpeed doesn't matter, Concentration matters.\n\n- Rana\n|\nMy Soul is my Guide, for my Soul is of that Abode I will not Speak of the Earthly, I am of the Unknown.\n\n- Jalaluddin\n|\nI see what the joy is; it is the joy of always loving, it is the joy of losing my own life in love to others.\n\n- Andrew Murray, The Master's Indwelling\n|\nPeople living godly will dwell on high. Meaning wealth, honour, prosperity, fame, elevation, joy etc.\n\n- Sunday\n|\nI think that as soon as you think of yourself as a famous person or anything like that, you're objectifying yourself in some weird way.\n\n- Ethan\n|\nFrom those to whom privilege and o